item.title: By: Suzi
item.dc:creator: Suzi
item.description:
In reply to <a href="/urban-decay-revolution-lipstick-69/#comment-461">Sarah Cosper</a>.
Ooh, which shade was it, Shame? The darkest I've gone so far is Jilted. It's so pretty, all purple and iridescent. I don't know if I've got the lady balls to pull off anything darker. I got a 20% of coupon for Ulta this weekend that was actually valid on UD stuff...so I bought 3 more! I am now the proud owner of Catfight, Jilted, F-Bomb, and Naked. No more makeup for me this month though, I'm officially cutting myself off.

item.title: By: Suzi
item.dc:creator: Suzi
item.description: God, I love these lipsticks. I finally bought one in Naked, and I have the minis in 69, Catfight, and Anarchy. They are all fantastic. The color payoff is insane. I also love how nicely stained it leaves my lips as it wears off. Catfight is for sure my next full size purchase.
